<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٢٢٤٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حَمْزَة:</span> عبد الْوَاحِد بن حَمْزَة.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
